![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/c83462f8-166d-4c05-8361-0e800832fa48/Screenshot+2025-10-16+202848.png)

This week on the **Major Issues Podcast**, the hosts dive headfirst into _Peacemaker_ Season 2! With James Gunn’s wild and unapologetic vision firing on all cylinders, the squad breaks down how the new season raises the stakes, deepens its characters, and somehow manages to be even bloodier, funnier, and more heartfelt than before. From Peacemaker’s ongoing identity crisis to the fallout of his complicated family ties, we unpack every explosive twist, emotional gut punch, and surprise cameo along the way. So grab your eagle and your favorite 80s hair metal track—it's time to talk about the most chaotic hero in the DC Universe!

Please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us wherever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the only stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.

Send us feedback at **ComicBookClique@Gmail.com!** You Are Worthy! 

